##Dataset 4

This dataset recorded which area of the room Micah cleaned or straightened up each day over one year.

**Do This:**
1. Open **[Dataset #4](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/13PTrN6QvdRMy4bGRudxJsD_NykH5tPHmgs2sMvP3O2I/edit?usp=drivesdk)**
2. Explore the dataset and the visualization by clicking the tabs on the bottom of the spreadsheet.
3. Discuss and answer the questions in your activity guide with your partner.
